# Changelog

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## [0.5.0] Beta
### Added
- Comprehensive test suite with 80%+ coverage target
- Test runner with coverage reporting support
- Integration tests for complete workflows
- Unit tests for all core functionality

### Changed
- Standardized version numbers across all files to 0.5.0
- Updated project status from Alpha to Beta
- Improved error handling with proper HTTP status codes

### Fixed
- Removed hardcoded absolute file paths from production code
- Fixed error page generation to use embedded HTML instead of external files
- Improved 404 handling for unmatched routes

### Removed
- Incomplete `aeon add` command functionality
- References to package registry features (moved to v1.0.0)
- Hardcoded development paths in Connection.cpp

## [0.0.2] Alpha


## [0.0.1] Alpha
### Added
- Wildcard path
- send file
- Initial alpha release of Aether.
- Basic project structure and `aeon` CLI.


---

## Legend
- **Added**: New features or functionality.
- **Changed**: Changes to existing features.
- **Deprecated**: Features to be removed in future releases.
- **Removed**: Features removed in this version.
- **Fixed**: Bug fixes.
- **Security**: Security-related updates.